nodes.text: Ina'irolia'kleoni was a Chiss Lieutenant Commander in the Chiss Ascendancy during the Cold War between the Galactic Republic and the resurgent Sith Empire. The pilot of Imperial Starship 2423T6H3L5, Ina'irolia'kleoni's name was used by a smuggler to falsify ship records and board the Imperial treasury ship King's Ransom.
